Thinta uQalisa" ukuqalisa insizakalo yeselula yakho manje. (Kungathatha imizuzu embalwa.)
Noma thinta"Yeqa ukuhlela ithebhulethi yakho usebenzisa uxhumano lwe-WiFi kunaloko.

"Kuze kube wenza kusebenze, izinto eziningi eziqukethwe yithebhulethi yakho ngeke zisebenze.
Uma uncamela ukweqa manje, ungenza kusebenze esikhathini esizayo Ezilungiselelweni."

"Insizakalo yedatha yeselula ayenzekanga isebenze. Lokhu kungaba inkinga yesikhashana.
Uma uncamela ukweqa manje, qinisekisa ukuthi ukwenza kusebenze ngesikhathi esizayo Ezilungiselelweni. Kuze kube uzenza kusebenze, izinto eziningi eziqukethwe yithebhulethieke ngekezisebenze."
Insizakalo yedatha yeselula yakho ayikwazanga ukwenziwa isebenze. Lokhu kungaba inkinga yesikhashana, futhi ingaxazululwa ngokuthi ucishe uphinde uvule ithebhulethi yakho.

Kwenzeke iphutha elidinga ukucisha nokuqalisa kabusha ithebhulethi yakho ngaphambi kokuba kwenziwe omunye umzamo wokwenza kusebenze. Ithebhulethi yakho izocisha ngokuzenzakalelayo kumasekhondi angama-60, noma ungathinta u-Cisha manje".
Emva kokuthi ithebhulethi yakho iishe, cindezela inkinobho yayo Yamandla ukuyiqalisa phansi."
Lethebhulethi isebenzisa igama lakho ukwenza ezinye izinsiza zibe ezakho siqu.

"Uyavuma ukuthi ithebhulethi yakho yamukela iphinde ifake ukuthuthukisa okuvela kwa-Google.
